
-- lets-ga.setup:

-- ds.page: Bin Finder
theme-switcher: false
fastn-badge: false
inset: $ds.spaces.inset-square.zero
background.solid: #ffffff
align-content: center
spacing: $ds.spaces.vertical-gap.space-between
inset if { ftd.device == "mobile" }: $ds.spaces.inset-wide.medium
document-image: https://i.postimg.cc/XJt7tnVX/UNWASTE-LOGO.png

Not sure where to throw your waste? Use our Bin Finder to quickly search any household item and know if it belongs in Wet, Dry, Reject, or E-Waste bins.

-- ftd.row:
margin-top.px: 24
spacing.fixed.px: 50
spacing.fixed.px if { ftd.device == "mobile" }: 24

-- ftd.image:
src: $assets.files.assets.hasiru-dala.unwaste-logo.png
width.fixed.px if { ftd.device == "mobile" }: 110
width.fixed.px: 183

-- ftd.image:
src: $assets.files.assets.hasiru-dala.hdi-logo.png
width.fixed.px if { ftd.device == "mobile" }: 74
width.fixed.px: 120

-- end: ftd.row

-- ftd.column:
width: fill-container
align-content: top-center
spacing.fixed.px: 24

-- ftd.text: Not sure where to throw your waste? Search below and find out.
classes: tagline


-- search:

-- end: ftd.column

